c: 3
v: 152
t: "Gom…óii Alla Goonginanii on Fodoore Makko nden tuma nde warayno…óon …ďe e DuŇčayee Makko, haa nde cooy…óon lurru…óon e fiyaake …óen, yeddu…óon …ďaawo o hollii on ko yi…óu…óon. No e mon …ďen faalaa…ďe aduna, no e mon kadi …ďen faalaa…ďe laakara. Hooti O Yiili on e ma…ď…ďe fii yo O Ndaarndo on. Gom…óii O Yaafanike on. Alla ko Jom ∆Āural e dow gom…óim…ďe …ďen"